# BFHL API

REST API for VIT Full Stack Assignment

## Setup
1. Install dependencies: `npm install`
2. Update your personal details in server.js
3. Start server: `npm start`

## API Endpoint
POST /bfhl - Main processing endpoint

## Test
Run `npm test` to test the API locally